Name: Shoot Them
About the game: A group of beautiful girls seemingly harmless to human beings and animals are actually clone female soldiers transformed by war scientists. They are not afraid of pain or death. They can smell the breath of the target a hundred miles away. As an enlisted human warrior, you are used to verify the actual combat performance of these clone female soldiers. In this prison simulation city, only one person can live... The game includes: Three different enemies of beautiful girls Two different maps More than 10 different levels Infinite Mode：The enemy is infinite,So,shoot them ALL! Crazy Mode:Every Enemy have diffirent size,So,shoot them ALL! If you love the game! Thanks for support us. And We will make more Levels
